CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A11, reads: "Meet the Springers - Brilliant Young Couple Manages to Combine Marriage and Career! - Stepping Out - Eric assists his wife with her wrap as they prepare to 'step out' on the town for the evening. - All Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing tuxedo, placing coat over woman's shoulders, in domestic interior with mobile hanging from ceiling, stereo, and rectangular patterned rug
